Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:07.90,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}9年前 高倉家·起居室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.61,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}颱風之夜。陽毬發高燒 很嚴重。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:07.90,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}打電話給醫院也只被冷冷地敷衍了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型颱風13號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從本州沿太平洋北上 現正經過關東地區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:18.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}西東京 中野區 杉並區 練馬區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在 請小心防範強風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護車全部都派出去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒的燒退不了啊 這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裏就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠葉! 回來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蠢材…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠葉!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.25,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}くるくるまわる　君の瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:05.07,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}探してまわる　駅のホーム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:10.16,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}響くファンファーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:13.36,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ガラガラ音をたてる街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.27,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}とりあえず　耳を貸してみたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:22.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　消えるはずの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.15,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:36.98,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もう二度と会えないような　そんな気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.35,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}運命が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.71,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}臨界点を突破してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:47.51,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}限界ならすでに去って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:52.84,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}絶対的支配だって　崩壊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:58.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}終末理論は机上の　空論でしかないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:09.29,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}0と1の世界線の果てから　叫ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:17.91,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　君が会いに来るような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:23.44,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕は目を閉じるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:02.25,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}轉啊轉 你的眼睛不停轉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:05.07,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在月台四處尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:10.16,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}號角聲在空中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:13.36,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}大街上轟轟作響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.27,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總之 先傾聽這聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:22.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在這個就要消逝的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.15,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:36.98,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總是覺得 我們無法再度相會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.35,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}命運也在嘲笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.71,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}突破臨界點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:47.51,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}極限已然消去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:52.84,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}就算被絕對地支配 也讓它崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:58.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}末日理論無非是一紙空談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:09.29,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在0與1的世界線的盡頭 呼喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:17.91,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總是覺得 你即將來與我相會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:23.44,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我 就閉上眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查結果很穩定 身體情況也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣再觀察一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不該這麼說 不過這真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹我們這行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會遇上極少數的病例 只能用奇跡來形容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹的情況正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於奇跡 我還有話想跟您說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能檢查一下這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 這個就是在陽毬身上發生奇跡的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是我的推測…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個帽子的真身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是外星生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個外星生命 用某種力量把陽毬的病…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 這也有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是嗎…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個很有趣的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 很有趣 這是很好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笑啊 「笑」!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑能增強免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在醫學領域裏也很重視其效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個帽子是從外星球來的啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣讓你妹妹每天都開懷大笑吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 得趕緊碾碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想工作的事情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託阿佐美小姐你做這麼難辦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是夏芽小姐的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起事故 真是不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你說除了知道有人推你下去 其他都不記得了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上… 那時候的事 我記不太清了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出事之前 我好像看到了什麼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了! 那個時候那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 看到那個了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏芽…小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是前幾天 在地鐵站內手扶梯上發生意外的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久寶阿佐美小姐的後續報道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久寶小姐對事故發生前後的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是她對警方提問做出的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方還在收集目擊者等相關信息 調查仍在進行當中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.73,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}早上好 我是雲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我是光莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.26,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我們兩人合起來就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Double Mayonname（註：mayonnaise+name的合成詞）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:46.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}搞錯啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我們兩人合起來就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.99,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Double Mayonnamassage（mayonnaise+name+message的合成詞）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.81,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不是這樣的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今天有什麼事呢 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上呢…冠葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 事情來得很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 說是要賣掉這座房子 但也不是馬上就怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 叔叔也會對你們負責 好好想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄養你們的親戚那裏 我也會打好招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過三人一起住可能就不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是病人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 還沒泡茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家會照顧好陽毬的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情會馬上告訴你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不想這麼說…冠葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的父母…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不會再回來這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢我會籌來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少錢才能不賣掉這個家?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠葉 再怎麼說我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 這不是你能籌到的數額啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要多少!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟爸爸約會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經不是小孩子了 感覺有點不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一句 我還沒跟爸爸提起過「他」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為爸爸會吃醋的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我現在 還想繼續做爸爸最心愛的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鮮咖喱午飯兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸吃這個可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南極特製芭菲 上面還有企鵝玩偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個也要一份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 改天再去那個水族館玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那個水族館」?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 跟媽媽一起三人經常去的 那個池袋的水族館
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸說企鵝的列隊行進很有趣 就把頭伸出通道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果不是被工作人員大罵了一頓嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的…麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還嚷著要親子三人配 所以買了一樣的企鵝手機鏈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 確實是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為蘋果很喜歡企鵝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸那時說 「蘋果 這就好像專門為你做的…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在跟女兒在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是定期的見面日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚上跟你吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話 讓你的女兒小藍也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人一樣的手機鏈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的「咖喱日」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己做的咖喱 給多蕗吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的任務還不算結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 接下來要給多蕗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 Merci
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.69,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：法語「謝謝」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的路上 帶著栗子蛋糕當禮物 去造訪多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗很喜歡吃栗子蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而拿著這個去的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定會令他陶醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這裏的 才是我心目中的「The Best of 栗子蛋糕」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗你真是fabulous max!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這味道…哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人陶醉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 好像被人盯著一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:10:00.71,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}9年前 暴風雨之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.50,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}那個時候冠葉發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.71,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}爸爸呢? 陽毬呢? 家人會變成什麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.47,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1072,253)}請有計劃{\fs35}地{\fs55}使用。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.47,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(1069,284)}注意{\fs18}不要{\fs25}使用{\fs18}過度。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢已收到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠回來得好晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不跟我們聯繫 到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計又是和女孩子在廝混吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要被花花公子冠葉菌傳染啦」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是正是 辛辛苦苦做的飯都要涼掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我們先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 荻野目同學回家太晚也不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我媽媽經常加班 很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不~是 是根本沒有等那種白癡老哥的必要!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶 這個土豆燒肉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是加了咖喱的土豆燒肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘋果的秘方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 想不到味道很搭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為「咖喱要和重要的人一起吃」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咖喱要和重要的人一起吃」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家是不放豌豆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 現在不說更待何時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 荻野目同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很誠懇地求你幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在觀察野鳥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著一本筆記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 那本筆記能借給我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用完了馬上就還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說蠢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非借給你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 絕對不借你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 那也不是能隨便借人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 那不過是單純的日程記事本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你看過了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然間瞄了一眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只不過是些計劃安排…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…話說 那都是你一廂情願的空想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是…命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本筆記上 寫著我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的命運日記
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命運日記」 這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我已經老實交代了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道那本筆記的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是之前從那個水族館買回來的紀念品?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太驚訝 好好聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 這帽子的真身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星生命!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個外星生命 命令我們把你的筆記…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是日記弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果違抗命令的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你別開玩笑了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當白癡嗎 我可是很認真在聽的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命運日記」什麼的 那才真叫莫名其妙好吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 「外星生命」又是什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦袋不是壞掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存 戰略!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine——!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知你等必將一事無成之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 啥? 啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算默不作聲聽你們說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你這頭母豬竟然肆意妄為胡言亂語
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀 陽毬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 趕緊把你那不可救藥的妄想排泄物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是那所謂的「命運日記」交給那邊的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 這什麼呀這是!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬 你究竟是怎麼了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子有問題的是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個跟蹤狂超變態女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬 你為什麼要說那麼過分的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸 竟敢跟我頂嘴 真是讓人噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個腦子爛透讓人作嘔的母豬婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太過分了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至於說到那個份上吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 下人 你也別在那發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去把那日記搶過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 雖然你是下了命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她都掉下去了 我想搶不是也搶不到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人當白癡啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 你都做了什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是陽毬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的卡車等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是頂帽子 太小題大做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛卡車!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這一天怎麼這麼悲劇啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 給我停住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:21.25,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}9年前 拂曉，颱風過境之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.95,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}冠葉與爸爸。那是男子漢之間的約定。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.25,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}那是成功男人的脊樑。所以我。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上沒有不會停息的暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果一直等到它停息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法保護重要的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記了 冠葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作起來 陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬…別死…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為那是頂普通的帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陽毬在開玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土豆燒肉呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 叔叔?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次說的錢 已經匯到你店子的賬戶裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼來源不明的錢 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以暫時住在這個家裏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:54.67,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}5{\fs30\pos(640,630)}TH STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:54.67,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.50,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おやじの靴を　はいてみた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:28.11,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}俺には　ちょっとキツイけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:31.86,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なかなか渋い音をだす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.52,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.51,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.95,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}トンガリ靴　はいたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:42.55,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ヤツと町を歩いたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:46.11,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恥ずかしそうに　笑い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.79,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping　Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.62,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:52.18,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうさ　これが　俺の
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:57.71,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}俺らの　おやじの靴さ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.47,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦り切れてて　キズだらけの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.81,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}古ボケた靴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.35,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おやじの靴が　ひかりだし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.96,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今じゃ　一番お気に入り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:17.46,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ビルの谷間で踊りだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.12,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.15,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:22.82,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stepping Slipping
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.31,insert_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's my Daddy's shoes
